lign=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"a, to the ninth power\"></span></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><br>For the exponential function <span class=\"italic\">f</span>, the table above shows several values of <span class=\"italic\">x</span> and their corresponding values of <span class=\"math_expression \"><span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"f of x\"></span></span>, where <span class=\"italic\">a</span> is a constant greater than 1. If <span class=\"italic\">k</span> is a constant and <span class=\"math_expression \"><span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"f of k, equals a, to the twenty ninth power\"></span></span>, what is the value of <span class=\"italic\">k </span>?</p></div></div>\n",
